dialogue: Oh my God, Rachel!
Hi!
Would you like some gum?
Are you alright?
Perfection?
Chandler, we've been here for an hour doing this! Now watch, it's easy.
No, you've got to whip it.
Well, this has been fun.
Hey!
You’ll never believe what just happened, Ross just totally blew me off and he didn’t even tell me why!
Y’know, thanks for trying to cheer me up, but I’m not gonna date some random guy from your work.

It’s probably because not mature enough. Or smart enough. Maybe he doesn’t like the way I dress—No that can’t be it. It’s really gotta be the smart thing. Oh I’m so stupid! I’m just like this incredibly pretty stupid girl!
You asked him too?!
Why?!
I don’t understand, do you want to go out with Ross?
You don’t want him, but you don’t want me to have him?
Hey! You have no right to tell me what to do.
Why are you so jealous of me?
Who?!

Rachel and I had a really big fight, can I come in? I-I mean I know we’re not supposed to see each other anymore and I’m okay with that, it’s just that I don’t know anybody in the city and I really need somebody to talk to about it.
But you know what might really cheer me up?
Seeing some more of your super-cool slides.
Totally, I love them! And, maybe you could finish telling me about all the different kinds of sand.
Oh great! Thanks Ross, you’re such a good friend!
Yeah. Ooh, I know what this is missing! Alcohol!
All right, I’m leaving! Because I’m not going to spend one more day with someone whose out to sabotage my every move. That’s you Rachel!
Oh my God, Rachel!
Hi!
And y’know what I said to him? "I’m gonna hire a lawyer and I’m gonna sue you and take all your money. Then I’m gonna cut you off!"
That he wouldn’t pay for my lawyer! Then he told me to come here and learn about the value of money from the one daughter he’s actually proud off.
Okay, I bought a boat.
Yeah but it wasn’t for me, it was for a friend.
Oh, that’s so great! Okay, I’m really gonna do this! I don’t know how to thank you guys.
Oh, Mr. Scientist has to get all technical!
So who made her queen of the world?
Hey!
Right! But, I am sorry.
She took all my stuff.
Oh my gosh, that was so lame. Like a pajmena could be a rug!
Were you this cute in high school?
No you stop!
You stop!
Oh no! But I just walked past three sales and I didn’t go in. How strong am I?
Yeah.
Me go out with Ross?! No! God no! What would make you think that?
No! I mean he’s nice.
He’s the kind of guy you’re friends with, y’know? But he’s not the kind of guy you date. He’s the kind of guy you’d date because you did. Me, not so much.
Oh no-no-no, he’s just I don’t know, he’s just a little bookish.
You think so too?
Fine, then let’s just say he’s not my type.
Well okay, if it means that much to you, then I’ll ask him out.
No! Y’know what Rachel? You’re right, y’know he has been really nice to me.
Yeah but maybe that’s a good thing. Y’know I’m doing all these different sorts of things, and maybe I should try dating a geek too!
What?
Really?!
It’s yours!
Hey!
